  "title": "Sales/ Key account Management (Electronic Manufacturing Services)",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities</p><ul><li><p>Expand the EMS business across Singapore, the Philippines, and Vietnam by securing project transfers and identifying new business opportunities.</p></li><li><p>Oversee the end-to-end sales process, coordinating closely with internal teams to ensure smooth project transition and execution.</p></li><li><p>Develop and maintain strong customer relationships, address operational concerns, and actively promote the company’s products and capabilities.</p></li><li><p>Prepare sales reports, market analysis, and performance updates for management review.</p></li><li><p>Represent the organization at trade shows, industry seminars, and outreach initiatives to strengthen brand visibility and market presence.<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma / Degree in Electronics Engineering</p></li><li><p>1–2 years of experience in the electronics industry, preferably in EMS sales;</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Sales driven, good attitude with customer service experience<br /></p></li></ul><p>Interested applicants for the above advertised position(s), please kindly click the <strong>APPLY </strong>button below or send in your updated resume to <a href=\"mailto:gs1@talenttradersg.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>salestrader@talenttradersg.com</strong></a><br /></p><p>EA License No.: 13C6305</p><p>Reg. No.: R1985956 (VIVIEN TAN)<br /></p><p>For candidate who applied for the advertised position is deemed to have consented to us that we may collect, use or disclose your personal information for purpose in connection with the services provided by us.</p>",
