    "description": "<p>TALENT TRADER GROUP PTE. LTD.</p>\n<p>Talent Trader is steered by young, dynamic professionals; each of them bringing their own vast experiences from leading Banks and HR Agencies.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We provide efficient talent sourcing, recruitment and retention services that help companies acquire effective Mid-management talent.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We offer the following value-added services for a variety of Mid-management positions across industry veticals such as Banking, Marine, Offshore, Retail, IT, F&amp;B, Education, Manufacturing and Others:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- <strong>Talent Sourcing and Recruitment</strong></p>\n<p>- <strong>International Recruitment</strong></p>\n<p>- <strong>Contract &amp; Temporary Staffing</strong></p>\n<p>- <strong>Payroll Services</strong></p>\n<p>- <strong>Employment Passes</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
